title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter should display in data set dialog
description: When in the query result page, no data is returned. The expected behavior is that the output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
OB: While in the query result page, there is no data returned.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
SR:
1. Open the query result page.
2. Execute the query.
3. Check if any data is returned.
4. Open the edit data set dialog and ensure the output parameter is displayed.
